        <item>
            <title>微軟 Copilot Search 挑戰 Google 搜尋地位，引入 AI 互動助用户延伸搜尋</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-copilot-search/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-copilot-search</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-copilot-search/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 03:00:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Search Engine]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301697</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="flex flex-1 grow basis-auto flex-col overflow-hidden"><div class="relative h-full"><div class="flex h-full flex-col overflow-y-auto [scrollbar-gutter:stable]"><div class="@thread-xl/thread:pt-header-height mt-1.5 flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-6" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 px-6"><div class="mx-auto flex flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn @xs/thread:px-0 @sm/thread:px-1.5 @md/thread:px-4"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="17613ce9-30aa-4a8e-be9b-7c3bba15671e" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p class="" data-start="103" data-end="269">Microsoft, 微軟正式在 Bing 搜尋中引入全新 AI 搜尋介面 Copilot Search，用户可透過 bing.com/copilotsearch 使用，獲得由人工智能生成的答案，並即時展開延伸提問或深入閲讀資料來源。這項設計與 Google 近期為搜尋引擎引入的 AI 模式互相呼應。</p><p data-start="103" data-end="269"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1-617x580.jpg" alt="" width="617" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1-617x580.jpg 617w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1.jpg 957w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 617px" /></p><p class="" data-start="271" data-end="397">Copilot Search 介面以簡潔首頁展示示範提問及搜尋欄，用户輸入查詢後，系統會彙整多個網上資料來源，產出 AI 回應，結果頁會出現「查看所有連結」與「查看推理」兩個按鈕。</p><p class="" data-start="503" data-end="616">針對偏好傳統網頁連結版面的使用者，Bing 仍保留原有搜尋功能。在自然語言提問時，搜尋結果頁上方會顯示名為 Copilot Answer 的段落，以 AI 模式快速呈現重點資訊，下方則列出常規網頁連結，提供一種混合式搜尋體驗。</p></div><p data-start="503" data-end="616">來源： <a href="https://dig.watch/updates/ai-powered-search-expands-with-microsofts-copilot-search">dig.watch</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
