            <title>【評測】vivo V50 詳細評測，主攝鏡成像佳 + 柔光燈表現更勝上代 + 拍攝功能多玩味濃 + 定價偏貴</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/04/vivo-v50-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vivo-v50-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/04/vivo-v50-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 13:30:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
