            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301507</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>vivo 早前除了推出旗艦手機 X200 系列外，近期亦發佈了新一代主打攝力的中階機 V50，依然保留了柔光環設計，同時加入了不少新功能，但使用起來感受如何呢？就讓 Edward 為大家實試一下吧。</p><h2>vivo V50 開箱直擊</h2><p>在為大家分享 vivo V50 的使用體驗前，先讓 Edward 為大家帶來它的開箱直擊吧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00848.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是 vivo 最新推出的中階手機 V50 的包裝盒。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00851.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者借得的版本是綢緞黑版，規格為 12GB RAM + 512GB ROM。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00855.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打開包裝盒，就已經見到 vivo V50 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00857.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00859.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中層就會見到一個半透明包裝袋，當中包含了手機保護套及説明書。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00862.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00864.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底層就會見到 SIM 卡槽針、USB-A to USB-C 數據電源線及 90W 電壓充電火牛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00868.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00870.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301522" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00891.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至此開箱完成，之後只要撕開手機的包裝袋，再長按開關鍵，就可以開啟電源並進行初始設定了。</p><h2>設計典雅手感不俗</h2><p>在設計上，vivo 今次推出的 V50 基本上與上代 V40 相比有九成相似，不過今次除了較沉實的灰黑色版（官方稱為綢緞黑）外，還設有採用紅色頗搶眼的安卡拉紅版，筆者就覺得外觀上後者相對地比較吸引。另外兩者除了顏色不同外，機揹物料亦有所不同：綢緞黑版採用的是複合板材，而安卡拉紅版就採用了玻璃物料，所以後者重量上會重了 10g，不過兩者重量也只是 200g 以下，而且機身厚度也只是 7.39mm（綢緞黑）/ 7.57mm（安卡拉紅），加上機背邊位及機面熒幕均是採用四弧邊設計，機身亦不算太闊，所以單手握機操控手感算是不錯，即使長時間握機使用仍然舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/011.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 設有兩種顏色版本：綢緞黑及安卡拉紅。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/051.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當中筆者覺得安卡拉紅會更加搶眼吸引，但它設計上較偏向女性化，而且因為機背採用了玻璃物料，所以會相對較厚及重一點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00874.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於綢緞黑版本就採用了複合板材作機背，相對地會較薄及輕，但設計上就比較平實，而且較為中性化，較適合男士使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00884.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身中框採用了拋光效果的金屬物料製造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00882.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於邊位方面，無論是機面熒幕還是機背均採用四弧邊設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301529" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00931.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00930.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00932.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲加上機身算輕及薄，所以長時間單手握機問題不大，單手握機操控或打字亦十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00935.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而由於機面機背邊位均採用弧邊設計，所以即使緊握機身亦不覺有界手感，頗為舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00899.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 採用了光學熒幕下指紋解鎖技術，解鎖靈敏度亦算高。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00896.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00893.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身右側設有開關鍵及音量鍵，而機底就設有內置喇叭、USB-C 插槽及 SIM 卡槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲V50 預載了 vivo 自家的 Funtouch OS 15 作業系統。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301537 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-1.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301538 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-2.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301539 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-3.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1301540 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4-262x580.jpg" alt="" width="262" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4-262x580.jpg 262w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/screenshot_20250402_-4.jpg 406w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 262px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面設計上與其他 vivo 手機分別不大。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
